      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-preserved example of a modern luxury sedan that has been treated with the utmost care. The exterior finish glows with a deep luster, showing only the occasional minor stone chip consistent with careful highway use. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin where the leather remains supple and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracks. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the premium navigation system, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound; it has followed a strict maintenance schedule, with recent service records including a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The tires have excellent tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a turn-key vehicle that offers a premium driving experience for someone who appreciates a car that has been genuinely loved and maintained.",
      "price": 34850.0,
