    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a well-maintained E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit retains its high-revving character with a crisp 8,400 RPM redline and linear power delivery. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from M-specific subframe reinforcement and a functional carbon fiber roof for a lower center of gravity. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and the M Variable Differential Lock. Recent service includes preventative maintenance on the throttle actuators and a fresh fluid flush. The suspension geometry is stock, providing an authentic, feedback-rich driving experience. Cosmetically solid with minor patina consistent with its mileage, this M3 is a driver-focused example ready for the B-roads.",
